body:
So me and my brother plays on the same PC and it's a pretty low end old model, though it can run smooth enough with low settings.

The weird part is whenever my brother logs in and try to play his, the client ( we're both using legacy ) lags and every game that starts ( after champ select, on the rift ) he has to exit the client and log in again.

When I use it and or after he reconnects its 31 ping and 70-100 fps consistently but if he doesn't reconnect his ping goes fluctuating from 50-70 making it spike a bit and only goes to 50-70 fps. We checked everything and all our settings are identical.{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}
